reviewText: This is a must-have DVD for anyone who carries. I paid full price, no compensation for a review, I simply believe I have become better at protecting myself and my family, and I have learned many skills and tactics I had never considered before. Well worth the price.
I use this in my classes and it is very good.  Everyone who carries a gun should watch this video.
I've watched a lot of these videos so I seen mostly things i knew, anyone who owns a gun should have a few books and videos on safety and tactics in their collection.
